content_text: My role model My role model is Lord Krishna. Krishna have taught us how to be generous and truthful, to be truthful and see how people will understand you, take you to the right path. He taught us how to St. people very politely an honestly to follow the pipes part of rice cuteness. This is how people will understand you and nothing evil will happen to you. If you follow the path of ideas knus Lord Krishna itself will help you to understand others problem. You need to listen to them. You should not interrupt or disturb them live.
